Water heater 2 years new, washer and dryer, 3 years.  TWO underground parking spaces.  All exterior maintenace, snow removal, water, tennis and and pool access all included in dues! Convenient to Hampden, Mt. Washington and I83 for an easy connute to downtown or north to the county.
